Module HW08
Package common

Interface IChatAppReceiver

All Superinterfaces:
java.rmi.Remote
All Known Implementing Classes:
ChatAppReceiver
public interface IChatAppReceiver
extends java.rmi.Remote
An entity that has inbound and outbound message processing. This can be used to create a "receiver" in a chat room where a receiver is simply a remote entity that can send and receive messages and commands. Additionally, this interface extends Remote for you to make it as easy as possible to create stubs or proxies.
Author:
Group C
